NEW FILE: smali_classes2/com/wisky/modulenotemanager/ext/AiRenameHelper.smali

Static helper. `run(SidebarNoteFragment)` finds the first checked note,
grabs its fileName, and fires the existing fire-and-forget AI channel:

    WiskySystemApiManager.Companion.toAiPage(content, prompt, cmdList, true)

Same channel used by the built-in AI sub-items (整理内容 / 生成邮件 / …).
Launches the AI app with our prompt preloaded and auto-sends.

